# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID — create a GA4 property at
# https://analytics.google.com, then Admin → Data Streams → your web
# stream → the "G-XXXXXXXXXX" ID shown there.
#
# This is a public identifier, not a secret (it's visible in every GA4
# site's page source) — but it's still not committed as a real value here
# since it's environment-specific. Copy this file to .env and fill it in;
# analytics.js no-ops harmlessly if it's left unset.
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=
